---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="Learn about Main Street Logic - our history, mission, and the small businesses we serve."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-light-bg to-soft-gray dark:from-dark-bg dark:to-navy py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-navy dark:text-soft-gray mb-6">
        Technology that works for your business
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-navy/70 dark:text-soft-gray/70">
        We believe every small business deserves access to smart, practical
        technology solutions.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Story Section -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy dark:text-soft-gray mb-6">Our Story</h2>
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-navy/80 dark:text-soft-gray/80 space-y-4">
        <p>
          Main Street Logic was founded with a simple idea: small businesses
          shouldn't have to navigate the complex world of technology alone. Too
          often, we saw local businesses struggling with outdated systems,
          paying for software they didn't need, or missing opportunities because
          they didn't know what was possible.
        </p>
        <p>
          We started by helping a few local businesses in our community. Word
          spread, and we realized there was a real need for technology
          consulting that speaks the language of small business owners - not
          tech jargon, but practical solutions that make sense.
        </p>
        <p>
          Today, we work with small businesses across the country, helping them
          make smart technology decisions that save time, reduce costs, and set
          them up for growth.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What We Do Section -->
  <section class="bg-white dark:bg-navy py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy dark:text-soft-gray mb-6">What We Do</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-navy dark:text-soft-gray mb-3">We Listen First</h3>
          <p class="text-navy/70 dark:text-soft-gray/70">
            Every business is different. We start by understanding your unique
            challenges, goals, and constraints before recommending any solution.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-navy dark:text-soft-gray mb-3">
            We Keep It Simple
          </h3>
          <p class="text-navy/70 dark:text-soft-gray/70">
            Technology should make your life easier, not harder. We focus on
            solutions that are practical, maintainable, and actually get used.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-navy dark:text-soft-gray mb-3">
            We Think Long-Term
          </h3>
          <p class="text-navy/70 dark:text-soft-gray/70">
            We're not here to sell you something and disappear. We build
            relationships and help you plan for the future.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-navy dark:text-soft-gray mb-3">We Stay Honest</h3>
          <p class="text-navy/70 dark:text-soft-gray/70">
            If you don't need something, we'll tell you. Our job is to help you
            make the best decision, even if that means doing nothing.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Locations Section -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy dark:text-soft-gray mb-6">Where We Work</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-navy/70 dark:text-soft-gray/70 mb-8">
        We work with small businesses across the United States. Most of our work
        is done remotely, which means we can help you no matter where you're
        located. For local clients, we're happy to meet in person when it makes
        sense.
      </p>
      <div class="bg-soft-gray/30 dark:bg-navy/50 rounded-lg p-6">
        <p class="text-navy/70 dark:text-soft-gray/70">
          <strong class="text-navy dark:text-soft-gray">Based in:</strong> The beautiful Pacific Northwest<br
          />
          <strong class="text-navy dark:text-soft-gray">Serving:</strong> Small businesses everywhere
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="bg-navy py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Let's work together</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-white/70 mb-8">
        Ready to see how we can help your business? Get in touch.
      </p>
      <a
        href="/contact"
        class="inline-block bg-steel-blue text-white font-medium rounded-md px-8 py-4 hover:bg-medium-steel transition-colors no-underline"
      >
        Contact Us
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
